=== SHADOW_STALKER ===
# id: 98
# title: The Shadow Stalker
# chinese_title: 暗影猎手
# category: Creature
# mode: dungeon

Something moves in the darkness just beyond your light's reach. You catch glimpses — too many legs, reflective eyes, a body that seems to absorb light. It doesn't attack, but it follows, matching your pace with predatory patience. Your scanner identifies it as a Drift-touched apex predator.

* [Stand your ground and make yourself look large]
  ~ gain_radical("大")
  "勇" (yǒng) — brave, courage. Stand tall like "大" (dà) — big.
* [Leave food as a distraction and slip away]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "逃" (táo) — to escape, to flee
* [Try to communicate — it seems intelligent]
  ~ gain_radical("犬")
  "兽" (shòu) — beast, animal. The radical "犬" (quǎn) means dog/animal.
* [Prepare for a fight]
  ~ start_fight
  "猎" (liè) — to hunt
